divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving tonight at the specific time listed, 9:12 pm. I could not judge the direction. It moved towards the mountain range (Franklin Mountains). Very fast, very bright, on the larger side, since I could see it through the city lights. The sky was clear. It may have not been a UFO, but I cannot identify it. I had no particular feelings at the time. I work as a delivery driver, and was returning from a delivery from Ft. Bliss, coming across the bridge from the gate. When I saw the object, I remembered to write down the time when I next stopped. I am not sure if anyone else noticed it.
